This directory has files that define the types used in the framework.

The files are:

Assert.hpp(.cpp) - Defines the assert functions
CAssert.hpp(.cpp) - Defines C compatible assert functions
BasicTypes.hpp - Type definitions for basic types (32-bit int, etc)
Serializable.hpp(.cpp) - Base classes and helpers for serialization classes
PolyType.hpp(.cpp) - Polymorphic type used to hold values of different basic types
StringType.hpp(.cpp) - Base class for strings used in the architecture
EightyCharString.hpp(.cpp) - string class with eighty characters for use by developers
StructSerializable.hpp(.cpp) - template class for wrapping already defined structs and making them serializable - NOT working yet